item.title: Non-Italian Carbonara
item.description: Easy to make delicious and creamy spaghetti carbonara dish. Kids love it and great for your next party! INGREDIENTS: 500 grams Spaghetti 250 grams bacon, cut into strips 100 grams button mushroom 2-3 cloves garlic 1 onion 2 eggs cooking cream parsley salt & black pepper Ingredients for making non-Italian carbonara
